// ║  🏭 Biorefinery Simulation: Process Design and Optimization                 ║
// ║  🌱 Life Cycle Assessment: Environmental Impact Analysis                    ║
// ║  💰 Techno-Economic Analysis: Cost and Profitability Assessment            ║
